     <div type="to_the_author">
   <head>To the Author.</head>
   <l>
      <hi>VErtue</hi> thine <hi>Obiect, thou</hi> her <hi>Subiect</hi> art;</l>
   <l>
      <hi>Thou</hi> deck'st <hi>her</hi> in thy <hi>verse, she</hi> decks thine heart:</l>
   <l>Each th' other doth deseruedly set foorth;</l>
   <l>From <hi>thee</hi> her <hi>praises</hi> flow, from <hi>her</hi> thy <hi>woorth.</hi>
   </l>
   <signed>R. C.</signed>
</div>
